en_662423_0	Today is the 3rd day of the Fast launched by MP Venerable Athuraliye Rathana Thera.
en_662423_1	He launched the Fast demanding to remove Minister Rishad Bathiudeen, Governors Asath Sali and M.L.A.M. Hisbulla from their portfolios.
en_662423_2	He has staged the Fast near the Sri Dalada Maligawa in Kandy.
en_662423_3	Meanwhile Parliamentarian S. Viyaalendran has also launched a Fast supporting Venerable Athuraliye Rathana Thera.
en_662423_4	Former Minister of the Eastern Provincial Council R. Thurairathnam and a group of people have joined the Fast which is being held in front of the Mahathma Ghandi School in Batticaloe.
